We also have a lot of
questions from you.

00:21:13.030 --> 00:21:15.370
Liz and her staff
solicited your questions.

00:21:15.370 --> 00:21:16.580
I have them here.

00:21:16.580 --> 00:21:19.400
I will inject those questions,
Liz, at the right moment.

00:21:19.400 --> 00:21:22.060
I thought it was right
to lead with Anne-Marie.

00:21:22.060 --> 00:21:25.300
In her position as state
working for Secretary Clinton,

00:21:25.300 --> 00:21:28.060
she had to look out
over the whole world

00:21:28.060 --> 00:21:31.220
and think about our
broad national strategy.

00:21:31.220 --> 00:21:34.720
I just suggested,
Anne-Marie, that we are--

00:21:34.720 --> 00:21:37.240
that we've fallen
from grace, that we

00:21:37.240 --> 00:21:40.360
