00:21:53.980 --> 00:21:54.980
- Yes.

00:21:54.980 --> 00:21:57.340
- But let me just
begin by saying

00:21:57.340 --> 00:21:59.150
how honored I am to be here.

00:21:59.150 --> 00:22:02.320
And I have to say when I walked
in with that trumpet fanfare,

00:22:02.320 --> 00:22:04.990
I thought I was at
the royal wedding.

00:22:04.990 --> 00:22:07.630
But the hats aren't
quite as good.

00:22:07.630 --> 00:22:11.330
I also am here as an
example of a glass ceiling

00:22:11.330 --> 00:22:13.360
that Secretary Clinton broke.

00:22:13.360 --> 00:22:16.810
I was the first woman Director
of Policy Planning, which

00:22:16.810 --> 00:22:18.855
is the big think job in
the State Department,

00:22:18.855 --> 00:22:22.270
and it was founded when
George Marshall asked

00:22:22.270 --> 00:22:24.310
George Kennan to
take it on, which

00:22:24.310 --> 00:22:26.740
is the legacy none of us
have ever lived up to.

00:22:26.740 --> 00:22:30.460
But Secretary Clinton
very deliberately

00:22:30.460 --> 00:22:32.020
wanted to prove to the world--

00:22:32.020 --> 00:22:34.240
I hope she did, I'm not
going to claim that-- but she

00:22:34.240 --> 00:22:36.520
wanted to prove that a
woman could hold that job,

00:22:36.520 --> 00:22:39.010
and that's why I'm
sitting here today.

00:22:39.010 --> 00:22:40.030
I would go anywhere.

