Unlike many others
on this stage,

00:30:19.440 --> 00:30:23.130
I have not had the opportunity
to work for Secretary Clinton,

00:30:23.130 --> 00:30:26.790
but I have benefited from
her career as a citizen most

00:30:26.790 --> 00:30:29.640
importantly and all the good
that she's done but also

00:30:29.640 --> 00:30:32.820
as a woman because she has
fought many fights that I

00:30:32.820 --> 00:30:35.830
will not have to fight
because she did that.

00:30:35.830 --> 00:30:37.167
So I want to thank you.

